    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Bhagavad Gita, Chapter XV


        Krishna:

        Men call the
        Aswattha,--the Banyan-tree,--

        Which hath its boughs beneath, its
        roots above,--

        The ever-holy tree. Yea! for its leaves

        Are
        green and waving hymns which whisper Truth!

        Who knows the Aswattha,
        knows Veds, and all.


        Its branches shoot to heaven and sink to earth,

        Even
        as the deeds of men, which take their birth

        From qualities: its
        silver sprays and blooms,

        And all the eager verdure of its girth,

        Leap
        to quick life at kiss of sun and air,

        As men''s lives quicken to
        the temptings fair

        Of wooing sense: its hanging rootlets seek

        The
        soil beneath, helping to hold it there,'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5431834928911583797, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6ff40fcf18efb134287c72f3785e2bc7, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 5902464882853280731, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: instanceId
      value: deb23b0a-5739-41c8-aa38-586660c92daf
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082410, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: The tree under which the Buddha attained enlightenment was a sacred
        fig; known ever after as the Bodhi tree, from bodhi, "awakening."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082416, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Bhagavad Gita Chapter 10 Verse 26

        Amongst trees I am the peepal
        tree (sacred fig tree); of the celestial sages I am Narad. Amongst the gandharvas
        I am Chitrath, and amongst the siddhas I am sage Kapil.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6181259333930047258, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GsplatAsset
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 4599839170941234424, guid: 85a11cf4ca5d41c4f8b34634739345ad, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 6181259333930047258, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_assetGuid
      value: 85a11cf4ca5d41c4f8b34634739345ad
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6835627233580907840, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dd81917df20a69b4298201e81c136e13, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 7173199714940506848, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Demeter an the Domestication of Figs

        The greek goddes Demeter
        was offered hospitality by Phytalus while searching for her daugher. As a
        thank you for his kindness she taught him the domestication of figs,'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7417057368276200879, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b468d01805473fa4da7c021719aeed71, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 8810918796485297829, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d70e4a31e4b62d8429bd22f81ae2d9e3, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 9161542878112791018, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Quran \u2013 95. At-Tin (The Fig)\n1.By the fig and the olive \u02F9of
        Jerusalem\u02FA, 2.and Mount Sinai, 3.and this secure city \u02F9of Mecca\u02FA!1
        4.Indeed, We created humans in the best form. 5.But We will reduce them to
        the lowest of the low \u02F9in Hell\u02FA, 6.except those who believe and
        do good\u2014they will have a never-ending reward. 7.Now, what makes you
        deny the \u02F9final\u02FA Judgment? 8.Is Allah not the most just of all
        judges?\n\n\u0648\u064E\u0671\u0644\u062A\u0650\u0651\u064A\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064E\u0671\u0644\u0632\u064E\u0651\u064A\u0652\u062A\u064F\u0648\u0646\u0650
        \u0661 \u0648\u064E\u0637\u064F\u0648\u0631\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064A\u0646\u0650\u064A\u0646\u064E
        \u0662 \u0648\u064E\u0647\u064E\u0640\u0670\u0630\u064E\u0627 \u0671\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064E\u0644\u064E\u062F\u0650
        \u0671\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064E\u0645\u0650\u064A\u0646\u0650 \u0663 \u0644\u064E\u0642\u064E\u062F\u0652
        \u062E\u064E\u0644\u064E\u0642\u0652\u0646\u064E\u0627 \u0671\u0644\u0652\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0633\u064E\u0640\u0670\u0646\u064E
        \u0641\u0650\u0649\u0653 \u0623\u064E\u062D\u0652\u0633\u064E\u0646\u0650
        \u062A\u064E\u0642\u0652\u0648\u0650\u064A\u0645\u064D\u06E2 \u0664 \u062B\u064F\u0645\u064E\u0651
        \u0631\u064E\u062F\u064E\u062F\u0652\u0646\u064E\u0640\u0670\u0647\u064F
        \u0623\u064E\u0633\u0652\u0641\u064E\u0644\u064E \u0633\u064E\u0640\u0670\u0641\u0650\u0644\u0650\u064A\u0646\u064E
        \u0665 \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064E\u0651\u0627 \u0671\u0644\u064E\u0651\u0630\u0650\u064A\u0646\u064E
        \u0621\u064E\u0627\u0645\u064E\u0646\u064F\u0648\u0627\u06DF \u0648\u064E\u0639\u064E\u0645\u0650\u0644\u064F\u0648\u0627\u06DF
        \u0671\u0644\u0635\u064E\u0651\u0640\u0670\u0644\u0650\u062D\u064E\u0640\u0670\u062A\u0650
        \u0641\u064E\u0644\u064E\u0647\u064F\u0645\u0652 \u0623\u064E\u062C\u0652\u0631\u064C
        \u063A\u064E\u064A\u0652\u0631\u064F \u0645\u064E\u0645\u0652\u0646\u064F\u0648\u0646\u064D\u06E2
        \u0666 \u0641\u064E\u0645\u064E\u0627 \u064A\u064F\u0643\u064E\u0630\u0650\u0651\u0628\u064F\u0643\u064E
        \u0628\u064E\u0639\u0652\u062F\u064F \u0628\u0650\u0671\u0644\u062F\u0650\u0651\u064A\u0646\u0650
        \u0667 \u0623\u064E\u0644\u064E\u064A\u0652\u0633\u064E \u0671\u0644\u0644\u064E\u0651\u0647\u064F
        \u0628\u0650\u0623\u064E\u062D\u0652\u0643\u064E\u0645\u0650 \u0671\u0644\u0652\u062D\u064E\u0640\u0670\u0643\u0650\u0645\u0650\u064A\u0646\u064E
        \u0668"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
